〈'''화(火花)'''〉（{{lang-en|"HWAA"}}）是韓國[[女子組合|女子組合]][[(G)I-DLE|(G)I-DLE]]的单曲，於2021年1月11日作为组合第四张迷你专辑《[[I_burn|I burn]]》的第二首歌曲兼主打歌，由[[Cube娱乐|Cube娱乐]]和[[联众唱片|联众唱片]]发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newdaily.co.kr/site/data/html/2021/01/11/2021011100225.html|script-title=ko:[포토] 4번째 미니앨범 '아이 번'으로 컴백한 여자아이들|trans-title=[Photo] (G)Idle making a comeback with the 4th mini album'I Burn'|publisher=New Daily|first=Sang-yoon|last=Jeong|date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-01-14|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115041042/http://www.newdaily.co.kr/site/data/html/2021/01/11/2021011100225.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲原版组合成员[[田小娟|田小娟]]创作，原版英语歌词由唱作歌手{{tsl|en|Phildel|Phildel}}创作，Pop Time担任共同制作人。歌曲的灵感出自小娟和组合成员叶舒华在一次交谈中提到的“冬日女孩”。她被这个想法吸引中，构想了女子受困于冬日的概念<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eFe6ocZWY5E|script-title=ko:본인등판 with (여자)아이들((G)I-DLE) full ver. /[Day6의 키스 더 라디오] kbs 210113 방송|publisher=KBS Cool FM's Day6's Kiss the Radio|via=YouTube|date=2021-01-14|access-date=2021-01-16|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115222646/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eFe6ocZWY5E|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

歌曲用“花”这个含糊意象表达情侣分手的感觉<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wowtv.co.kr/NewsCenter/News/Read?articleId=A202012310028&t=NN|script-title=ko:(여자)아이들, 미니 4집 `I burn` 트랙리스트 공개…전곡 자작곡|trans-title=(G)Idle, 4th mini album'I burn' track list released... All self-composed songs|last=Yoo|first=Byung-cheol|publisher=Korea Economic Daily|date=2020-12-31|access-date=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128133847/https://www.wowtv.co.kr/NewsCenter/News/Read?articleId=A202012310028&t=NN|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以寒冬中熊熊燃烧的烟火及绚烂多彩的花朵，感性地比喻爱的痛苦<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pop.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=202101111556282409510_1|script-title=ko:(여자)아이들, 미니 4집 `I burn` 트랙리스트 공개…전곡 자작곡|trans-title=[Overall]'Han (一)' and connected" 'Comeback' (G)Idle, So Yeon's cool farewell song|last=Kim|first=Nayul|publisher=Herald Pop|date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128133855/http://pop.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=202101111556282409510_1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://pop.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=202101111705542776169_1|script-title=ko:[팝's신곡]"못다 한 원망도 훨훨 타리"‥(여자)아이들, 차가운 이별 '화(火花)'|trans-title=[Pop's new song] "The resentment that I couldn't do" ......(Female) children, cold farewell'Fire|last=Kim|first=Nayul|publisher=Herald Pop|date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-01-14|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116082052/http://pop.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=202101111705542776169_1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。音乐层面上，歌曲主要采用[[蒙巴顿|蒙巴顿]]风格，融入{{le|暗黑音乐|Darkness in music|黑暗流行}}、[[梦幻流行|梦幻流行]]和[[合成器流行|合成器流行]]的风格，编排中加入{{tsl|en|Music of Asia|亚洲音乐|东方乐器}}，将火和花两个[[双关语|双关语]]融入令人上瘾的重复点及逐渐变化的歌词<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wowtv.co.kr/NewsCenter/News/Read?articleId=A202101070029|script-title=ko:‘컴백 D-4’ (여자)아이들, 미니 4집 `I burn` 오디오 티저 공개…다채로운 총 6곡 수록|trans-title='Comeback D-4' (G)Idle, 4th mini album'I burn' audio teaser released... 6 songs in total|last=Yoo|first=Byung-cheol|publisher=Korea Economic Daily|date=2021-01-07|access-date=2021-01-14|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116085313/https://www.wowtv.co.kr/NewsCenter/News/Read?articleId=A202101070029|dead-url=no}}</ref>，延续〈[[HANN_(Alone)|HANN (Alone)]]〉（2018）和〈HANN (Alone in winter)〉（2021）的剧情<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slist.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=217294|script-title=ko:(여자)아이들 수진 "신곡 '한(寒)', 디지털싱글 '한(一)'과 비슷하지만 전혀 ...|trans-title=(G)I-dle Soojin "New song 'Han (寒)', Digital Single 'One (一)', but not ...|last=Kim|first=Nayeon|publisher=Single List|date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112191945/http://www.slist.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=217294|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲音乐视频由VM Project Architecture的Paranoid Paradigm执导，歌曲上线当天于组合YouTube频道同步公开。

歌曲空降韩国[[Melon|Melon]]排行榜首位，是第四代偶像组合首支头位打榜的歌曲<ref name="4th">{{cite web|url=http://en.koreaportal.com/articles/47702/20210112/g-i-dle-melon-chart-idol-group-track-album.htm|title=(G)I-DLE Is First 4th-Generation Idol Group To Debut At #1 On Melon Chart|work=Korea Portal|first=Starlene|last=Portillo|date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112230743/http://en.koreaportal.com/articles/47702/20210112/g-i-dle-melon-chart-idol-group-track-album.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>；在[[Gaon單曲榜|Gaon單曲榜]]最高排第4名，是组合首支排进前五的热门单曲，也是他们在Gaon下载榜的首支冠军歌曲。歌曲在《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》榜单也取得不俗的成绩，位列[[韩流百强单曲榜|韩流百强单曲榜]]第5位、{{le|全球数字歌曲销量榜|World Digital Song Sales}}第8位、[[公告牌全球二百强单曲榜|全球二百强单曲榜]]第173位。

