== 歌名 ==
歌名〈HWAA〉有花的意思，象征春天和爱情<ref name="scmp">{{cite web|url=https://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/k-pop/bands/article/3117869/gi-dle-members-talk-about-break-ups-new-k-pop-album-i-burn|title=(G)I-dle members talk about break-ups, new K-pop album I Burn, and how it reflects their musical and emotional growth|work=South China Morning Post|last=Tamar|first=Herman|date=2021-01-16|access-date=2021-01-17|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117130345/https://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/k-pop/bands/article/3117869/gi-dle-members-talk-about-break-ups-new-k-pop-album-i-burn|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而中文“[[火部|火]]”和“[[华姓|花]]”在韩语中均发“hwaa”音，但两个字在汉语普通话中的音调不同<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/art/2021/01/732_302358.html|title=(G)I-DLE creating splash with new song 'Hwaa'|work=The Korea Times|last=Dong|first=Sun-hwa|date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116041720/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/art/2021/01/732_302358.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。小娟表示：“我之所以把这两个hwaa放在一起，是想表达歌曲的主人翁虽处在寒冬中，但能够用火焰驱散寒冷，像花一样绽放自己，给寒冬带来一丝春色。”而焰火在韩语中的就是“火花”，她藉此希望这张专辑能够大获成功，“绽放绚烂的焰火”<ref name="scmp"/>。

== 背景 ==
在《[[美丽佳人|美丽佳人韩国版]]》2021年1月刊的采访中，田小娟暗示这首歌曲“和冬天很般配，但也不只给人寒冷的感觉。可能会有点冷，但有些地方会很火热？就好像在一间开着暖气的房间盖着厚毛毯，但窗户开着，只能你的脸能感受到寒冷<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kang|first=Ye-sol|date=2020-12-22|script-title=ko:솔직한 (여자) 아이들|trans-title=Honest (G)I-dle|url=http://www.marieclairekorea.com/celebrity/2020/12/frankly/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231120632/http://www.marieclairekorea.com/celebrity/2020/12/frankly/|archive-date=2020-12-31|access-date=2020-12-31|work=Marie Claire Korea|language=ko}}</ref>。”歌曲是(G)I-DLE的第二首分手歌曲，透露出分手时寒冬一样冷彻心扉的氛围<ref name="cube">{{cite web|url=http://www.cubeent.co.kr/gidlealbum/4236219|title=(G)I-DLE - I burn album information|publisher=Cube Entertainment|date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113080554/http://www.cubeent.co.kr/gidlealbum/4236219|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{Quote|quote=《[[I_burn|I burn]]》出现了三种意象，第一种‘冬天’代表分手后冻人的情感，第二种“火”代表融化那些情绪的欲望，第三种‘花’代表分手前冷漠但美好的爱情。这幅途径从受困于寒冬的女性开始。我希望将‘冬天’、‘火’和‘花’构筑在‘Hwaa’这个词中，展现克服分手的伤痛后完全绽放自我的概念。我们认为，与其传达特定的概念，不如用更多精力思考传达这些情感的最佳方式。尽管我们是跨国团体，我们还是希望传达出分手这种情感，这种放之四海而皆准的情感。我希望这些情感给人小说的感觉。|author=(G)I-DLE提及歌曲的概念|source=《韩国经济日报》<ref name="Hankyung">{{cite web|url=https://www.hankyung.com/entertainment/article/202101110021H|script-title=ko:(여자)아이들, 한 겨울 불꽃 같은 컴백…'화'로 음원 1위 노린다 [종합]|trans-title=(G)IDLE, comeback like a winter fireworks... Aiming for No. 1 music source with'Tue' [Overall]|first=Soo-young|last=Kim|publisher=Korea Economic Daily|date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-11|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115213158/https://www.hankyung.com/entertainment/article/202101110021H|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}

[[Minnie|Minnie]]坦白说，她有一段时间不是很明白用泰语怎么表达〈HANN (Alone)〉所蕴含的意思<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sedaily.com/NewsView/22H7R61JN2|script-title=ko:[SE★현장] "1년 아껴둔 곡" (여자)아이들의 필살기, 역시 독보적(종합)|trans-title=[SE★Site] "A song saved for a year" (G)I-dle's special moves are also unique|first=Seung-hyeon|last=Cho|publisher=Seoul Economic Daily|date=2021-01-12|access-date=2021-01-14|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115195451/https://www.sedaily.com/NewsView/22H7R61JN2|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但和其他成员交谈完，她明白了爱情和分手的含义：“我努力表达我对分离的感受，因为这在每个国家都是相似的<ref name="SS"/>。”歌曲舞蹈融入{{le|剑舞|sword dance}}动作<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sports.donga.com/article/all/20210111/104871012/1|script-title=ko:[DA포토](여자)아이들,환상적인 칼군무|trans-title=[DA photo] (G)I-dle, fantastic sword group dance|work=Sports Donga|date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-01-14|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115033606/https://sports.donga.com/article/all/20210111/104871012/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由编舞Hyunzzinii和表演导演金世焕导演<ref name="ss">{{cite news|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/CJ5wzi6jCBY/|title=(여자)아이들 '화(火花)(HWAA)' [쇼케이스무대영상]|website=Instagram|date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-01-16}}</ref>。Minnie在[[SBS_(韩国)|SBS原创节目]]《HANBAM》中透露，小娟在她们参加[[Mnet|Mnet]]生存节目《[[Queendom|Queendom]]》演唱〈{{tsl|en|Lion ((G)I-dle song)|Lion (歌曲)|Lion}}〉之后，在〈[[DUMDi_DUMDi|DUMDi DUMDi]]〉之前写了这首歌<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaLbUIOiVF8|title=Fire' on the stage and'Fire' behind the stage (G)I-DLE Kung-Chak Chemie - Pre-disclosure|publisher=한밤 HANBAM|via=YouTube|date=2021-01-13|access-date=2021-01-14|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113115148/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaLbUIOiVF8|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之后等到冬天发布<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elitedaily.com/p/gi-dles-i-burn-is-the-breakup-album-everyone-needs-in-their-life-exclusive-51015715|title=(G)I-DLE's 'I Burn' Is The Breakup Album Everyone Needs In Their Life — EXCLUSIVE|work=Elite Daily|last