===梗概===
[[File:(G)I-dle_-_Hwaa.jpg|thumb]]
影片开头，一棵树从郁郁葱葱迅速变得枯萎扭曲，组合的成员们在树的面前<ref name="mvgood">{{cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=438&aid=0000032543|script-title=ko:[뮤비가 좋다] (여자)아이들의 한이 담긴 꽃 한 송이, '화'|trans-title=[MV is good] (G)I-dle, A flower filled with children's han,'hwa'|publisher=KBS Media|first=Ji-eun|last=Jung|date=2021-01-13|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128134106/https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=438&aid=0000032543|dead-url=no}}</ref>。薇娟、Minnie、小娟、穗珍、雨琦和舒华展现出强烈的眼神交流，稍微表达对分别伴侣的怨恨<ref name="mvgood"/>。薇娟以[[姬髮式|姬髮式]]示人<ref name="mvgood"/>，雨琦则戴着一顶假短发<ref name="hair">{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsworldi.com/newsView/20210111513930|script-title=ko:(여자)아이들 우기 “평생 첫 단발…MV 촬영 땐 가발로”|trans-title=(G)I-dle Yuqi, "First short hair in my life… With a wig when shooting MV”|publisher=Sports World|first=Ga-young|last=Jeong|date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128134020/http://www.sportsworldi.com/newsView/20210111513930|dead-url=no}}</ref>，Minnie梳着亮红色直刘海，小娟一头银发，其他成员则留着发夹做成的非常规发型，并拿着雨伞和扇子等道具<ref name="mvgood"/>。成员们的服装蕴含“冬”、“火”和“花”三个视觉概念<ref name="tease1">{{cite web|url=http://www.stardailynews.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=289985|script-title=ko:'컴백 D-3' (여자)아이들, 미니 4집 타이틀곡 '화(火花)' 뮤직비디오 티저 영상 공개|trans-title='Comeback D-3' (G)I-DLE, the music video teaser video for the title song'Fire Flower' released|publisher=Star Daily|first=Seol-hwa|last=Chun|date=2021-01-08|access-date=2021-01-14|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115060316/http://www.stardailynews.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=289985|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tease2">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbnnews.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=457417|script-title=ko:(여자)아이들, 신곡 '화(火花)' 뮤직비디오 2차 티저 영상 공개|trans-title=(G)I-DLE, the second teaser video of the music video for the new song 'Fire Flower' released|publisher=NBNNews|first=Sung-hoon|last=Hong|date=2021-01-09|access-date=2021-01-14|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116010205/http://www.nbnnews.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=457417|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她们跳着舞，如同盛开的花朵，背后是仿造蓝色雪景的背景，小娟则在一个树窝里说唱<ref name="tease1"/><ref name="tease2"/><ref name="minji"/>。“火、燃烧和盛开”三个词连续出现，咒语一般，用火化开冰冻的心，带来鲜花盛开的春天<ref name=":3"/>。穗珍唱的第一段主歌结束后，副歌前段和副歌开始说明，只需要点燃一点花火，只需要盛开一朵花，就能够融化冰冻、被雪覆盖的心<ref name="Benedetta"/>。视频的最后，她们随着强烈的节目起舞<ref name="mvgood"/>。

===评价===
《时尚青少版》贝内塔塔·吉多赞扬歌曲的音乐视频，认为“歌曲的意义在这段宏伟且电影化的音乐视频中，得到壮美的展现，(G)I-DLE已经将这种效果练到炉火纯青了。小娟、薇娟、Minnie、穗珍、雨琦和舒华在寒冷荒凉的环境中穿行，然后演变成火红烈焰——她们的造型也和布景相得益彰，令人回想起东亚地区的传统服装和配饰<ref name="Benedetta"/>。”《Portal Popline》凯恩·奈恩斯（Caian Nunes）认为视频混搭了“自然元素和未来主义的建筑”，“各布景的丰富细节及服装令人着迷”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://portalpopline.com.br/gi-dle-mostra-superproducao-no-clipe-hwaa-novo-mini-album-i-burn/|title=(G)I-DLE mostra superprodução no clipe “HWAA” + novo mini-álbum “I Burn”|trans-title=(G)I-DLE shows overproduction in the video “HWAA” + new mini-album "I Burn"|language=pt|work=Portal Popline|first=Caian|last=Nunes|date=2021-01-11|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115210040/https://portalpopline.com.br/gi-dle-mostra-superproducao-no-clipe-hwaa-novo-mini-album-i-burn/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《The Standard Pop》娜塔蒙·康·莱（Nattamon Khom Loi）认为视频将深刻的音乐、琅琅上口的歌词及色彩对比分明的场景结合在一起，代表旱季过后鲜花盛开<ref name="standard"/>。《滚石印度》里迪·查克拉博蒂认为歌曲的音乐视频和《[[Oh_My_God|Oh My God]]》的音乐视频相似，“随着成员们拥抱自己的力量和能力，走出生活的试炼，色调从冷艳的蓝白色转换成炙热的红色”<ref name="RS"/>。

